{"data":[{"name":"107:1","price":"1. Heb je degenen gezien die de afrekening ontkent?","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يُكَذِّبُ بِٱلدِّينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6198,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"ara-ayta alladhī yukadhibu bil-dīni ","translations":["Have you seen","the one who","denies","the Judgment","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["ara-ayta","alladhī","yukadhibu","bil-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1010],[2,1010,1670],[3,1670,2990],[4,2990,6185]]}},{"name":"107:2","price":"2. Dat is degenen die (meedogenloos) de wees afstoot.","arabic":"فَذَٰلِكَ ٱلَّذِي يَدُعُّ ٱلۡيَتِيمَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6199,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhālika alladhī yaduʿʿu al-yatīma ","translations":["Then that","(is) the one who","repulses","the orphan","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhālika","alladhī","yaduʿʿu","al-yatīma",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1150],[2,1150,2000],[3,2000,2770],[4,2770,6435]]}},{"name":"107:3","price":"3. En niet (zichzelf noch anderen) aanspoort tot het voeden van de armen.","arabic":"وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَىٰ طَعَامِ ٱلۡمِسۡكِينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6200,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"walā yaḥuḍḍu ʿalā ṭaʿāmi al-mis'kīni ","translations":["And (does) not","feel the urge","to","feed","the poor","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","yaḥuḍḍu","ʿalā","ṭaʿāmi","al-mis'kīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,760],[2,760,1730],[3,1730,2240],[4,2240,3150],[5,3150,7145]]}},{"name":"107:4","price":"4. O wee, voor diegenen die (onachtzaam) in hun gebeden.","arabic":"فَوَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6201,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl","meta":{"transliteration":"fawaylun lil'muṣallīna ","translations":["So woe","to those who pray","(4)"],"translitera